Dạ em sửa lại ngay ạ, "Cài đặt" phải nằm ở trên, chữ bác sĩ nằm ngang, và thêm icon chatbot:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CliniCare - Admin Dashboard</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #E5E7EB;
        }

        .container {
            width: 1492px;
            height: 925px;
            display: flex;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            border-radius: 8px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Sidebar - 210px × 925px */
        .sidebar {
            width: 210px;
            height: 925px;
            background: #2F56C0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding: 0 16px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .logo-icon::before,
        .logo-icon::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background: #2F56C0;
        }

        .logo-icon::before {
            width: 14px;
            height: 2.5px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .logo-icon::after {
            width: 2.5px;
            height: 14px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .menu {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2px;
            padding: 0 12px;
        }

        .menu-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: white;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: left;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            opacity: 0.7;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .menu-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .menu-item.active {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .menu-item svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .menu-divider {
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background: #F5F6F8;
        }

        /* Top Navigation - 64px */
        .top-nav {
            height: 64px;
            background: white;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .top-nav-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .top-nav-logo-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .top-nav-logo-icon::before,
        .top-nav-logo-icon::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background: #111827;
        }

        .top-nav-logo-icon::before {
            width: 12px;
            height: 2.2px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .top-nav-logo-icon::after {
            width: 2.2px;
            height: 12px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .top-nav-logo-text {
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .top-nav-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .search-bar {
            position: relative;
        }

        .search-bar input {
            width: 280px;
            padding: 8px 16px 8px 36px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            background: #F9FAFB;
            color: #111827;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .search-bar input::placeholder {
            color: #99A1AF;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .search-bar input:focus {
            border-color: #2F56C0;
            background: white;
        }

        .search-icon {
            position: absolute;
            left: 12px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
        }

        .notification-btn {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .notification-btn:hover {
            background: #F3F4F6;
        }

        .user-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .user-avatar {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #111827;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .user-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #111827;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Content Area */
        .content {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        /* Greeting Section */
        .greeting-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .greeting h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .greeting p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6B7280;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: white;
            color: #111827;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: #F9FAFB;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #2F56C0;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #2847A0;
        }

        /* Stats Grid */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
        }

        .stat-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6B7280;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .stat-icon svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .stat-change {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .stat-change.positive {
            color: #10B981;
        }

        .stat-change.negative {
            color: #EF4444;
        }

        .stat-change.neutral {
            color: #6B7280;
        }

        /* Bottom Grid */
        .bottom-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
        }

        .card-header {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Appointment List */
        .appointment-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .appointment-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .appointment-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .appointment-info {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .appointment-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .appointment-details {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6B7280;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .appointment-status {
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .appointment-status.confirmed {
            background: #D1FAE5;
            color: #065F46;
        }

        .appointment-status.pending {
            background: #FEF3C7;
            color: #92400E;
        }

        /* Doctor List */
        .doctor-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .doctor-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .doctor-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .doctor-info {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .doctor-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .doctor-specialty {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6B7280;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .doctor-status {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .doctor-status.active {
            background: #10B981;
        }

        .doctor-status.busy {
            background: #F59E0B;
        }

        /* Activity List */
        .activity-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .activity-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: start;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .activity-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .activity-icon svg {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
        }

        .activity-info {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .activity-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .activity-time {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Chart Container */
        .chart-container {
            height: 200px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .chart-svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        /* Chatbot Button */
        .chatbot-button {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 24px;
            right: 24px;
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            background: #2F56C0;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(47, 86, 192, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.2s;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .chatbot-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(47, 86, 192, 0.4);
        }

        .chatbot-button svg {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
